description: Under the temptation of the massive volume of the industry, ThunderStone, as the online entertainment industry with the most extensive coverage of the crowd and the game industry where blockchains are most likely to settle first, will focus on the R&D and release of the top blockchain games all over the world in the future. TST Token is a decentralized blockchain application token based on ERC20 created by ThunderStone. TST will become the universal Cryptocurrency standard within the ThunderStone game ecosystem Its total circulation is three billion pieces.
name: ThunderStone
